TheifStall(“silk stall”, “and recieve 100k”, 100, 20*playerLevel[17], 995, 10000, 30, 0x340);
^Defines ^Name ^Message Lvl Needed^ ^Exp Rate(20) Item^ ^Amount (Leave The 30, 0x340)

[code]case 2562:
TheifStall(“gem stall”, “and recieve 50k”, 60, 125*playerLevel[17], 995, 50000, 30, 0x340);
break;

case 4878:
TheifStall(“scimitar stall”, “and recieve 10k”, 20, 100*playerLevel[17], 995, 1000, 30, 0x340);
break;

case 4877:
TheifStall(“magic stall”, “and recieve 25k”, 40, 125*playerLevel[17], 995, 25000, 30, 0x340);
break;

case 4876:
TheifStall(“general stall”, “and recieve 5k”, 1, 70*playerLevel[17], 995, 5000, 15, 0x340);
break;

case 2560:
TheifStall(“silk stall”, “and recieve 100k”, 100, 20*playerLevel[17], 995, 10000, 30, 0x340);
break;

case 2565:
TheifStall(“silver stall”, “and recieve 35k”, 80, 150*playerLevel[17], 995, 25000, 30, 0x340);
break;[/code]
